Subject: Buses By the Beach Camping Registration Info

Hello Fellow Volks Folks,
Buses By the Beach is hosting it's forth annual Bus Benefit May 19-21st in
Grand Rapids, MI. This event keeps getting larger every year. To help us
plan how much space we are going to require, it is very helpful to make a
reservation. Please be sure to tell Grandrogue Campground you are with the
Buses By the Beach group. You can contact them at 616-361-1053.

For more information about the campground please visit:
http://www.grandrogue.com/

For more information about Buses By the Beach's events:
http://www.busesbythebeach.com/

Wishing you many miles of smiles in your VW!
The Volks Folks at Buses By the Beach
